<plot>Looking to add trendy color to a dull white room? Want to merge two people's stuff into a single space and make it all look terrific? Shopping for a sofa but don't have a clue what you need to know before you buy? This is the perfect show for you. Area is the practical, exciting and up-to-the-moment home-design series that will inspire you to live well. Join host Lise Simms as she shares hot products, top values, basic decorating ideas, insider tips and much more--all geared to make your home look great.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?045026</url></doc>
